{"id": "214", "post": "<div class=\"post-214 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-virtual-servers tag-germany tag-xen tag-xencon-net\" id=\"post-214\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/xencon-48mb-xen-vps-for-499-euro/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Xencon \u2013 48MB Xen VPS for 4.99 Euro</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/germany/\" rel=\"tag\">germany</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/xen/\" rel=\"tag\">xen</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/xencon-net/\" rel=\"tag\">xencon.net</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> March 26, 2009 @ 11:59 pm, by LowEndAdmin</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/images/xencon.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"/media/images/xencon.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"188\" alt=\"Xencon\" class=\"screenshot litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> You though <a href=\"/blog/yes-you-can-run-18-static-sites-on-a-64mb-link-1-vps/\">running websites on 64MB Xen VPS</a> was a challenge? How does <b>48MB</b> sound? <a href=\"http://www.xencon.net/\">X|encon</a>, a German VPS company, has its base <a href=\"http://www.xencon.net/xentry_vserver\">x|entry Server</a> starting at 4.99 Euro with just the challenge you want! For around USD$6.75/month, you get</p><ul><li>48MB memory</li><li>5GB storage</li><li>10GB/month data transfer</li><li>Xen</li></ul><p>It has some pretty interesting features in its own control panel. The almost-realtime bandwidth-management is pretty amazing. You can even play astro shooting game inside the control panel while waiting for your VPS